  <!-- EN: APW-1 Anti-Materiel Rifle -->
  <RNGun_APW1_AMR.label>APW-1反器材步枪</RNGun_APW1_AMR.label>
  <!-- EN: The APW-1 Anti-Materiel Rifle is a semi-automatic precision weapon chambered in 12.5mm, designed for long-range engagements against armored targets. Featuring adjustable optics and powerful armor-penetrating rounds, it excels at neutralizing vehicles and heavy enemies. Reliable and versatile, it’s a critical tool for Helldivers in tactical combat scenarios. -->
  <RNGun_APW1_AMR.description>APW-1反器材步枪是一款大口径狙击步枪，它配备可调节光学瞄准镜和强大的穿甲弹，在远程距离可有效对付轻型载具装甲。它性能可靠，用途广泛，是绝地潜兵在作战中的关键武器。</RNGun_APW1_AMR.description>
